      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione status scadenza for- *
      *                          * nitore                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rr-dat-bcm           to   w-det-srd-scf-drd      .
           perform   det-srd-scf-000      thru det-srd-scf-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Tests                               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Su status scadenza              *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-det-srd-scf-sts    not  = "A"
                     go to stp-srt-inp-220.
