      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-sfs-cod-fnt       to   w-let-arc-dcf-fnt      .
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-dpz      .
           perform   let-arc-dcf-000      thru let-arc-dcf-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su codice nazione              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-naz    =    "IT "
                     go to stp-srt-inp-220.
