      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sfs-dtr-rgs       >    w-det-srd-scf-drd
                     move  "N"            to   w-det-srd-scf-sts
                     go to det-srd-scf-999.
       det-srd-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
